dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Outagamie County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'Outagamie_Hydro_2019_Line' and 'Outagamie_Hydro_2019_Poly'.Line: [This is a line feature class identifying the location of all non-navigable and navigable water within Outagamie County. It is a county-wide file including all USGS designated navigable waterways and all non-navigable waterways.]Poly: [This is a polygon feature class that corresponds with navigable streams within Outagamie County. This feature class represents the larger areas of the Navigable Streams.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
